    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>2019/6/18 毕业典礼，因为懒，图片都没有P就放上来了。</p><a id="more"></a><iframe frameborder="no" border="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" width="330" height="86" src="//music.163.com/outchain/player?type=2&id=26090155&auto=1&height=66"></iframe><p>农大的钟矗立在公寓楼前，显得非常的庄严，夜晚往往有情侣坐在台阶上窃窃私语。</p><p><img src="http://i2.tiimg.com/640680/bfdda048f2cf1e6a.jpg" alt="Markdown"></p><p><img src="http://i2.tiimg.com/640680/f6d728f084c23276.jpg" alt="Markdown"></p><p><img src="http://i2.tiimg.com/640680/51e7bfc6aa196c6b.jpg" alt="Markdown"></p><p>这片树荫下的唯一缺点就是夏天有好多蚊子~<br><img src="http://i1.fuimg.com/640680/8951d76a92e49373.png" alt="Markdown"></p><p>拗大长腿<br><img src="http://i1.fuimg.com/640680/988af9bcf127646d.png" alt="Markdown"></p><p>照照镜子<br><img src="http://i1.fuimg.com/640680/56cdd5d463476a74.jpg" alt="Markdown"></p><p><img src="http://i2.tiimg.com/640680/767b306de5a60010.jpg" alt="Markdown"></p><p>大家看我毕业啦<br><img src="http://i1.fuimg.com/640680/182be6394f939cdc.jpg" alt="Markdown"></p><p>上课的时候我总是想一件事：下课了我要吃什么<br><img src="http://i1.fuimg.com/640680/bb337313854d80d0.jpg" alt="Markdown"></p><p><img src="http://i2.tiimg.com/640680/a7690bb055620275.jpg" alt="Markdown"></p><p>谁不让我吃我就不理谁╭(╯^╰)╮<br><img src="http://i2.tiimg.com/640680/f0e89ea7b7a4adda.jpg" alt="Markdown"></p><p>下课啦，和我一起吃饭吧~<br><img src="http://i1.fuimg.com/640680/a89e2a6fa2f81cde.jpg" alt="Markdown"></p><p><img src="http://i1.fuimg.com/640680/c95cea0fea05faa6.jpg" alt="Markdown"></p><p>出发~<br><img src="http://i1.fuimg.com/640680/f670e5802f0cbb05.jpg" alt="Markdown"></p><p>下面我给大家表演一个</p><center><font color="red" ,font="" size="5">L~O~V~E~</font></center><p><img src="http://i1.fuimg.com/640680/392b93ab9f40a3b4.jpg" alt="Markdown"></p><p><img src="http://i1.fuimg.com/640680/ba41d806699d10b2.jpg" alt="Markdown"></p><p><img src="http://i1.fuimg.com/640680/7239844b5ce5844b.jpg" alt="Markdown"></p><p><img src="http://i1.fuimg.com/640680/7cfcad05a8749f6b.jpg" alt="Markdown"></p><p>装作很矜持地拍一张✧(≖ ◡ ≖✿)嘿嘿<br><img src="http://i2.tiimg.com/640680/4cbb224c7b50a4f0.jpg" alt="Markdown"></p><p>我要第一个上去拍~<br><img src="http://i2.tiimg.com/640680/4e1efaf3544860d6.jpg" alt="Markdown"></p><p><img src="http://i2.tiimg.com/640680/549546b998b0693f.jpg" alt="Markdown"></p><p><img src="http://i2.tiimg.com/640680/be9bd57d2457c034.jpg" alt="Markdown"></p><p>看镜头啦<br><img src="http://i1.fuimg.com/640680/149763fc6d552c90.jpg" alt="Markdown"></p><p>可是指的地方也不对耶<br><img src="http://i1.fuimg.com/640680/10edfd016604f594.jpg" alt="Markdown"></p><p>这次对啦<br><img src="http://i1.fuimg.com/640680/bb49c9cbe1ab7585.jpg" alt="Markdown"></p><p>什么，学完经济还是不会买花花绿绿的股票<br><img src="http://i1.fuimg.com/640680/3ba76543ec8d54a6.jpg" alt="Markdown"></p><p><img src="http://i1.fuimg.com/640680/cef463aff57a56e6.jpg" alt="Markdown"></p><p>好热呀，终于可以脱帽子了<br><img src="http://i1.fuimg.com/640680/5dbb7958ab39a322.jpg" alt="Markdown"></p><p>毕业啦~谢谢大家~<br><img src="http://i1.fuimg.com/640680/1592ab4de8bda3ea.jpg" alt="Markdown"></p><center><font color="pink" ,font="" size="5">Congratulations on my dear girl friend Mengmeng~</font></center><p>附：<br>毕业论文~</p><div class="row">    <embed src="https://www.cmwonderland.com/blog/mengmeng_thesis.pdf" width="100%" height="550" type="application/pdf"></div><p><strong>感谢：照相和整理的男票</strong></p>]]></content>
    
